Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果樓主係local u grad<br />\n可以去試吓big4<br />\n死捱三年再跳出去個條件已經係好好多<br />\n大把公司請big4人<br />\n期間睇吓你考唔考到個牌<br />\n跳出去做super/accountant應該都冇問題<br />\n我IVE hd+ topup degree, 想入都難<br />\n每一步都係血汗</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我係cheap u grad 既<br />\n一入職就係d 得3個人既cpa firm 做... 人工低到喊...係之後考左牌先入左去second tier 做...先發覺local cpa d 野完全冇用...所以入去做果時好辛苦<br />\nd 野又唔識，senipr又expect 你做到，所以真係做足7/24..."},{"pid":"11ce321f292110d612368c3e282a4766e32bfff3","tid":105413,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T04:05:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Ipo 周期就黎完<br />\n各位睇路</blockquote><br />\n咩係ipo"},{"pid":"036ca098184d3fda19c895d9517ecb75a748d9f4","tid":105413,"uid":3017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T04:20:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Ipo 周期就黎完<br />\n各位睇路</blockquote><br />\n咩係ipo</blockquote><br />\n屌 自己google下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4178ae7084a0993887d32111c879f7fdbf5c6026","tid":105413,"uid":73092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T05:01:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Ipo 周期就黎完<br />\n各位睇路</blockquote><br />\n咩係ipo</blockquote><br />\ninternet public orientation"},{"pid":"1abf8437297a8fdb2be6eb1d8e8c278246908c10","tid":105413,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T05:03:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Ipo 周期就黎完<br />\n各位睇路</blockquote><br />\n咩係ipo</blockquote><br />\ninternet public orientation</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b99d126b53dba6053be39a89b400f5500d6a22ae","tid":105413,"uid":17684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T05:09:48.000Z","msg":"做左幾廿年會計同你講，唔考到個牌、無大陸經驗、唔係4大出黎；搵大公司工真係窄窄地。<br />\n重有&hellip;要識得用多幾個軟件例如SAP, Flex, Orical, Excel (advance level)... 唔係都係窄窄地。<br />\n<br />\n最重要就係&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n係大部份公司入面，通常有好野會計部通常排最後，人工加得永遠最少，但加班就係最多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔加班就成公司當你怪獸咁睇。<br />\n<br />\n而家零願接多幾份freelance 都好過做份長工。超碼多d私人時間，人工只係爭果少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"747e638772013b712dbed5ee183645f22f71e4a1","tid":105413,"uid":26976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T05:14:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做左幾廿年會計同你講，唔考到個牌、無大陸經驗、唔係4大出黎；搵大公司工真係窄窄地。<br />\n重有&hellip;要識得用多幾個軟件例如SAP, Flex, Orical, Excel (advance level)... 唔係都係窄窄地。<br />\n<br />\n最重要就係&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n係大部份公司入面，通常有好野會計部通常排最後，人工加得永遠最少，但加班就係最多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔加班就成公司當你怪獸咁睇。<br />\n<br />\n而家零願接多幾份freelance 都好過做份長工。超碼多d私人時間，人工只係爭果少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n接咩freelance?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a159e31afb2b415144958133bee09d6817a7f3ae","tid":105413,"uid":17684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-04T05:23:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做左幾廿年會計同你講，唔考到個牌、無大陸經驗、唔係4大出黎；搵大公司工真係窄窄地。<br />\n重有&hellip;要識得用多幾個軟件例如SAP, Flex, Orical, Excel (advance level)... 唔係都係窄窄地。<br />\n<br />\n最重要就係&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n係大部份公司入面，通常有好野會計部通常排最後，人工加得永遠最少，但加班就係最多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔加班就成公司當你怪獸咁睇。<br />\n<br />\n而家零願接多幾份freelance 都好過做份長工。超碼多d私人時間，人工只係爭果少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n接咩freelance?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幫人&ldquo;按月理帳&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買套peachtree已經可以做到好多野。<br />\n但&hellip;<br />\n你一定要識d local firm至易搵到job<br />\n因為好多細公司佢地都唔想請會計，諗住俾audit firm做。但有d audit firm覺得無audit咁好搵，就會搵人接黎做，佢地就淨係做audit"}]}